Package: spINAR
Type: Package
Title: Estimation of semiparametric integer autoregressive models
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2023-01-16
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Maxime",
           family = "Faymonville",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "faymonville@statistik.tu-dortmund.de"),
    person(given = "Javiera",
           family = "Riffo",
           role = "aut",
           email = "javiera.riffo@tu-dortmund.de"),
    person(given = "Jonas",
           family = "Rieger",
           role = "aut",
           email = "rieger@statistik.tu-dortmund.de",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0007-4478")))
Maintainer: Maxime Faymonville <faymonville@statistik.tu-dortmund.de>
Description: A set of functions used for the following tasks.
    1. Simulate INAR(p) data with arbitrary innovation distributions (parametric family or probability mass function).
    2. Semiparametric estimation of INAR(p) model.
    3. Semiparametric INAR Boostrap.
    4. Fully parametric estimation of INAR(p) model.
    5. Penalized (semiparametric) estimation of INAR(p) model.
